have age and heart rate for 25 people. So nothing super sophisticated, but kind of interesting,

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:50.080
and then we give users the ability to download this synthetic dataset as a CSV file.

00:01:50.080 --> 00:01:56.599
If we go over to GitHub, we can find our code. So here is the repo. We have a README file,

