are where the OpenAI API key come to play. We're going to actually go ahead and call twice.

00:02:43.279 --> 00:02:47.279
So we're going to take our description from what the user said. We're going to say,

00:02:47.279 --> 00:02:52.399
generate a fake dataset with at least two variables as a CSV string based on the description

